{"h9d64db55g1653g4852ga871g68985f2e2571": ["I'm ready. Lower the trap.", "2c8537fb-bf73-43a2-a8ff-48e41453adea", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "1b550bb0-b2d7-45ee-54bb-d09c2b75e03c"], "h7d0c9ad0g9e7ag4159gb80agb424c80d1f36": ["I'm ready. Lower the trap.", "863d6788-5887-45c8-bafa-87128631904e", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "4096ea04-c0e6-0657-66b7-7e89ce83ff80"], "hccd9264ag32e2g45bbg815ag909626f7f98c": ["Lower the trap, Nymessa. This creature must die.", "863d6788-5887-45c8-bafa-87128631904e", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "9d6de32e-9833-5af3-42fb-fbc84bdca716"], "h7a897ea2g3165g4d59ga221gf24181d9e6bb": ["*Your skull pounds in response to the prisoner's white-hot stare. Her lips don't move, yet you hear her voice.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "6b20f489-19c0-e7a0-5b50-716206d677c3"], "h8e5fe208g87c6g44e7g9ad5ge294873a2257": ["<i>You again.</i>", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "93db4906-2103-a796-bed0-88eb6ec737b6"], "h23c761ecg755eg4bc3g89f6g0352658b92be": ["<i>Meet the prisoner's glare.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "dc5946f3-2515-35be-47f2-1a86bdc8be20"], "he2dea397gc028g4b0bg9b5ag5411c7d782b7": ["*Your skull briefly aches - and you are <i>her. </i>You feel her irritation and indignity.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "ed6fe3b1-1962-ec5c-b702-39423c094276"], "hf49958edg3dedg46b2gae11g3880099f0e93": ["*And you feel answers. She knows more about your condition.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "033857b0-809b-78fd-6204-43da20c92cc1"], "h132f11aegb8d5g489eg92bdg39766fffee4d": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "cacf131e-80c8-15e2-4c51-703cf24f9e80"], "h233ffc22gbc69g4900gafc1gbe8ae976bbd1": ["Zorru was right. Yellow as a toad, and twice as ugly.", "2c8537fb-bf73-43a2-a8ff-48e41453adea", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "df0f1625-d185-4975-0696-1ed262c43c19"], "h1f704e2cg0d73g460dg8d81g7dcb25c1c1f5": ["You're coming with me, 'fore... oh! Looks like I've got company.", "2c8537fb-bf73-43a2-a8ff-48e41453adea", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "e5e104c3-8aa6-4605-6764-f6e9e9a64c13"], "h1ad8bab0g2226g46fbg82cfg03666f83a6bf": ["*Your skull pounds in response to the prisoner's white-hot stare. Her lips don't move, yet you hear her voice.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "0f34527a-d0dd-2eb5-cb09-bcbc6620898d"], "h255aa1fdgb89cg4680g963cg65b1aa89f39b": ["<i>You. Get rid of her.</i>", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "7ccc2463-4566-11f8-dd60-91c69330a293"], "hcf6d83e7g6da7g4fcag9de5g8b0f7c822ae8": ["<i>A githyanki. She ought to be killed, here and now.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "1783541c-74c6-05ac-2026-fa68351a2131"], "hb8546ddbga089g4de6gb438g47ae7fd63551": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "2d2e9ee4-2a92-f3e0-8329-4c4e7fb88d44"], "hc40d05beg3b06g46c0g8823g3ee4835c9a2e": ["*Your skull aches before you can take a step - and you <i>are</i> the creature. You feel her irritation and indignity.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "4836525d-4302-563b-01b1-947aeef39188"], "h9642805bg6f8ag47ccgb172g8a8af16b3e55": ["This creature is dangerous. Get out of here - leave it to me!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "d16eddb0-aafd-b400-7177-415462439c68"], "h984db770gf9eeg4fcegbcfbge72647e050b0": ["You're right. I need to go check out that blast.", "2c8537fb-bf73-43a2-a8ff-48e41453adea", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "d0f1d112-8de1-3d24-0db3-cf80e7d4dae9"], "h87ce858agc75bg45c4g88b2gd62ec78b1f4f": ["A blast? Care to be more specific?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "d037954f-4c60-b084-3045-92e518044d1c"], "hd42620a3gaf9bg4945ga461g35250c407bc1": ["You didn't hear it? Shook our camp good, so I came for a look.", "2c8537fb-bf73-43a2-a8ff-48e41453adea", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "edba2bb8-5537-0b1f-8cf2-32e528de91c0"], "h4bcd8d81gd11ag457eg8e74g4814c4f4a3b1": ["I'm in dire need of healing. Where is this camp?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "d5c73f79-f1be-fc2f-aaf8-b70631335642"], "hf0838b0ag4de5g43deg9c20g082335bf5e22": ["North-west. Look for Nettie. Whatever your wound, she can mend it.", "2c8537fb-bf73-43a2-a8ff-48e41453adea", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "b1689a24-058e-76dc-761d-868ea36ab10e"], "h1fd26ea2gcc7ag4544g9a3bg06a067db832e": ["And be careful. There are goblin traps <i>everywhere.</i>", "2c8537fb-bf73-43a2-a8ff-48e41453adea", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "24826b48-d232-4611-6559-138007083afa"], "h80185f0dgda84g47d6g87ccgf3d3ef3f7174": ["Find refuge elsewhere. We've enough mouths to feed.", "2c8537fb-bf73-43a2-a8ff-48e41453adea", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "62477d54-f405-4598-ec90-55e49532bee0"], "h7fa05e97gdc0ag486dgb116g3b8bbe220341": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "35ab19a8-b385-66cf-8699-4ea765715183"], "hb4973f94g251dg4826g87e7g0279aedd10d9": ["No. I'm not leaving this fiend with a stranger.", "2c8537fb-bf73-43a2-a8ff-48e41453adea", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "12b22161-8843-af86-1ee6-833467d4f238"], "h25352e04g9a43g40c9gafcdg2334de439c45": ["Shoot the trap down. We must kill it before it harms someone.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "2797f2ec-8e29-c2ba-9928-d63e59e3ae6c"], "h3f63ad06gf947g441cgb9bbgcfce0d71e88b": ["You're right. No one's safe if that thing goes loose.", "2c8537fb-bf73-43a2-a8ff-48e41453adea", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "738307cb-0053-9615-3bd1-e4df39cb4369"], "hbea18ee2g3905g45d4g89e9g381d381a0e41": ["Lower the trap and ready yourself.", "2c8537fb-bf73-43a2-a8ff-48e41453adea", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "fc69fc6d-d682-0f0f-8034-f3dce5fb8b92"], "h87ada8b6ged9cg4b79gad90g04af846a601e": ["No. I'm taking it to camp. Zevlor will know what to do with it.", "2c8537fb-bf73-43a2-a8ff-48e41453adea", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "9ae271bb-36b7-febb-ca3d-c5eb297093ca"], "ha45ba05egae46g4468gb904g473453e03f95": ["<i>Kill her.</i>", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "402a0aed-cfdc-8a81-c991-0591fac53bc9"], "h525e70a4g75ecg451bgba85ge4134d922c1a": ["Shoot the trap down. I'll tear it apart before anyone else gets hurt.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "9f03da7c-e4f1-e142-2ea4-0fcc2c8b32ac"], "h161589f6g72c6g4f47ga8cbg3ed841e15d9e": ["<i>Attack the tiefling.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "f0a26ae0-0158-0cbd-dd7c-ee3b21e01d8b"], "h8e7493a9gc079g4d1ag8e7eg978077cf91c5": ["<i>Rat.</i>", "2c8537fb-bf73-43a2-a8ff-48e41453adea", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "e3be04e8-0691-8e50-e116-8f5b37160bb0"], "hff6d0abeg1960g4858g8ab0gb17c8f20f40f": ["<i>Coward.</i>", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "b62402d8-d9fb-7d8c-9a92-bf4eb62646df"], "h4f5b3aabgeefcg4282g973fg3c260ef775bb": ["You're with me, toad.", "2c8537fb-bf73-43a2-a8ff-48e41453adea", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "a504c36f-564e-b8b9-bec5-3cb07e95cf9a"], "h21da9d0egb014g4374g921age8a502c62baa": ["<i>You again. Get rid of her.</i>", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "b425742f-f9f0-e9d8-a5c2-82cd1df1fb68"], "h34361cf4g45c7g4372gb416g9478f4e98bfa": ["Holy hells. Another one.", "2c8537fb-bf73-43a2-a8ff-48e41453adea", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "52ad01f2-2c4c-6a39-4436-1adc21abcf21"], "haf723fe4g4686g4afaga7dagc042b3176edc": ["If you value your life, walk away.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "8b94bbef-db4a-4907-9a60-7f25acb059aa"], "h6ed1546eg41e5g4f9ag95feg3dabd5e01d4e": ["You needn't ask twice.", "2c8537fb-bf73-43a2-a8ff-48e41453adea", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "865cbbf2-9732-9056-4a0e-0dd8b6058651"], "hec1f207cgf166g4b99gb018g0c4f4fe8cda0": ["Not happening!", "2c8537fb-bf73-43a2-a8ff-48e41453adea", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "c425071f-8524-e588-bbc6-5bc5b97ef30e"], "hfdb45442gc669g4259g915ag18b32e3cfa2a": ["Holy hells. <i>Under-elf.</i>", "2c8537fb-bf73-43a2-a8ff-48e41453adea", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "b75f8a11-1fd5-cdc6-08ac-3f8700170c43"], "hb6442552gba4ag4a54g9e32g6ceb4a6514aa": ["Holy hells. <i>Under-dwarf.</i>", "2c8537fb-bf73-43a2-a8ff-48e41453adea", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "73b3ad55-58ff-3ccc-5550-751b2e2f9915"], "h7512bc2cg2eb6g4724gaf27g0bf171642c24": ["Zorru was right. Yellow as a toad, and twice as ugly.", "2c8537fb-bf73-43a2-a8ff-48e41453adea", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "f40d3710-810d-b86e-16ce-2d48f02f1731"], "h74d87ab4gde6bg4e29g9b13ga87d2340748b": ["Zorru was right. Yellow as a toad, and twice as ugly.", "2c8537fb-bf73-43a2-a8ff-48e41453adea", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "eaf605d7-03e3-9a5a-91bd-28357a9ee07e"], "hed5c8c8egf62dg4af5gbc49g564915511392": ["Zorru was right. Yellow as a toad, and twice as ugly.", "863d6788-5887-45c8-bafa-87128631904e", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "d71bbb2b-ba87-2e4f-cf94-7ce5e72f901e"], "h6d340fc5g4608g4989g8558gc695078e2330": ["You're coming with me, 'fore... oh! Looks like I've got company.", "863d6788-5887-45c8-bafa-87128631904e", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "9bbb01d7-d23f-bf04-d0ea-d149a6d9be9b"], "h8cbb4a4ag1bd9g4ea0g9655g837238aa36d8": ["<i>You. Get rid of him.</i>", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "f2db42b7-5fe0-af68-880e-56c5b88b9ad2"], "h7aab9a62g9b8eg4604gab40g05307873e66c": ["You abandoned me on the ship. Why should I help you?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "2b69c7b9-28a0-716b-82c8-db5aefdc2d4a"], "heb816682g50ddg4c2fg9ff8g8f77c5286ac8": ["*Your words flow to her, though you never speak them aloud.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "a5f23a4c-d1d1-5838-f1e8-c4f16bfafd0e"], "h16a79029gd169g4f18g8d64g9dd0cdca751d": ["<i>I know what grows inside you. And I know of a cure.</i>", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "171e6128-5120-bd04-6a6d-d7f327003623"], "h8c57cf2bg7166g4a27g8283g11fe642b1fad": ["Remember how keen she was to leave me to die on the nautiloid? We can't trust her.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "be7452e6-3ba9-6ac7-1664-43d042c7fa20"], "hba35d7b3g9b10g4fbegaab3gefaeb9f0f7e1": ["We can't trust her - think of what her kin did. Best if we just kill her right now.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "35cd8717-e198-9934-eec2-d81931bf76d5"], "h618e46aeg845dg4662g9bedg13f35e19d074": ["You abandoned me on the ship. Why should I help you?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "257123ab-35fb-6ab5-218c-3b2672e7fa07"], "h291f4836ga581g4391g9969g13e5fb6d36df": ["Rather demanding for a woman in your position. Why should I?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "307b8a79-b816-a115-5f3f-371b5e8b143d"], "h46c2dcc4g980ag4232gafceg8549a8eefeff": ["<i>A githyanki. She ought to be killed, here and now.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "b7b2b3a9-4773-fe33-581d-81a40102d323"], "h4f293ff3ge204g4fd8g8df6g90524e4dc8a1": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "45668101-6807-c52b-fa97-c5972e725929"], "h6dd63a2agee3fg4cd0g9d83g7fff430eba4c": ["This creature is dangerous. Get out of here - leave it to me!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "ccd88a6b-d364-383b-690e-93cd74455ac4"], "h17818da5g1b68g4635g9483g5e3250361f84": ["You're right. I need to go check out that blast.", "863d6788-5887-45c8-bafa-87128631904e", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "773bcebc-fc18-ce50-693a-7cbed469b561"], "h3c777c0ege11eg4294gb7f7gafe3efa2509a": ["A blast? Care to be more specific?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "5de3363d-a35a-4173-5ef3-6d283cf37773"], "hc8e2890fg75d9g4b3fg8b0cg2da3058650b0": ["You didn't hear it? Shook our camp good, so I came for a look.", "863d6788-5887-45c8-bafa-87128631904e", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "e7563ed8-be9c-9ac5-9f29-e9a0aaf18771"], "ha5e6dff4g039bg4b17g8480g7ed386238f7b": ["I'm in dire need of healing. Where is this camp?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "8d5dc3ec-5dbc-0021-6004-41fa6744c9f0"], "hbd11864dgf9c4g464cga572gf92b18f45e79": ["North-west. Look for Nettie. Whatever your wound, she can mend it.", "863d6788-5887-45c8-bafa-87128631904e", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "bd985410-fa6b-9eec-810e-09019595d79d"], "h3d00a897ga6e2g49bfgbdccgcb3e36392a75": ["And be careful. There are goblin traps <i>everywhere.</i>", "863d6788-5887-45c8-bafa-87128631904e", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "687e3149-887f-4977-96c7-0e57d9b9e55d"], "h63fc4e11gaf18g48f8g8297ga88771077589": ["Find refuge elsewhere. We've enough mouths to feed.", "863d6788-5887-45c8-bafa-87128631904e", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "9eb62384-83b1-7554-9992-c6aba2f5b18d"], "h2e8945c3g1efcg47bega099gb236b1d97c24": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "64cf35fb-754c-1ee2-d59c-ab1e3fa44ced"], "ha9755da2gb41cg43a5g80dcg80683a6191cb": ["No. I'm not leaving this fiend with a stranger.", "863d6788-5887-45c8-bafa-87128631904e", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "6c6df960-1917-6bcf-73c8-b45cb55eba1e"], "h6a5e3adegdd33g4ba1ga4e7gcf3e8c157c25": ["<i>Kill him.</i>", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "c28fb387-4074-52a7-a027-5043e19f8961"], "hacdf9dbegb997g4e0egb055g8ea172391bdd": ["Shoot the trap down. We must kill it before it harms someone.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "01426f6e-01d2-67bd-bfd8-0b6b37d2996b"], "hce011001g14f4g437eg951eg38ceaa4310b6": ["You're right. No one's safe if that thing goes loose.", "863d6788-5887-45c8-bafa-87128631904e", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "01569e5f-0d53-31a8-5d83-668b3438e2e1"], "h5d658866g2830g4f0bgaf8fg28389b92541c": ["Lower the trap and ready yourself.", "863d6788-5887-45c8-bafa-87128631904e", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "c0cec3be-6412-b399-e254-78faa00faad1"], "h02f7363cgccb8g4254g92ddg704e1e99ff76": ["No. I'm taking it to camp. Zevlor will know what to do with it.", "863d6788-5887-45c8-bafa-87128631904e", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "7e87af18-fcae-3154-e3dd-70b0f8380bb2"], "h8dd6c42agd6e0g4d06g915ege9c78a366405": ["Shoot the trap down. I'll tear it apart before anyone else gets hurt.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "5b3da83b-5e7a-b04e-254c-d99b635532a4"], "hdc4282f8gb8b1g4461ga0fdg468a95d271cd": ["<i>Attack the tiefling.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "f39e5620-ca1f-4190-4adc-0378df0d766c"], "h8b2cfaefg6298g49b4g8965g759f1e618aa3": ["<i>Rat.</i>", "863d6788-5887-45c8-bafa-87128631904e", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "21332736-2495-d58e-15bb-c1f5794743ad"], "h84e9f40dg64deg4541g9d98g68200af09936": ["You're with me, toad.", "863d6788-5887-45c8-bafa-87128631904e", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "c97e7648-2759-6c01-7eaf-30aabcf645f5"], "hdfe9c706g3940g4fb5gbfc4g6006753d5b90": ["<i>You again. Get rid of him.</i>", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "a7f58cec-ca6e-0116-ef8e-78c7a87dc32c"], "hb060a87eg62b4g43e6g92fbgcb7bb39cd837": ["Holy hells. Another one.", "863d6788-5887-45c8-bafa-87128631904e", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "6e4e8845-091d-d9a1-080d-0f4007c04331"], "h9db80aefgc0e6g426cg9a7dg1532d3be5a13": ["If you value your life, walk away.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "25fc3610-8fd7-9cff-2051-827b259cd7ec"], "h43cba5a1g2663g44c7g84dfg533427199caf": ["You needn't ask twice.", "863d6788-5887-45c8-bafa-87128631904e", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "71df2f3d-2828-b717-3826-70ae9c7a7f14"], "h6579c5b3g9c2ag4f53ga83fg085601449c62": ["Not happening!", "863d6788-5887-45c8-bafa-87128631904e", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "30c59e3d-4151-9bb5-cf89-6aaa07e73465"], "h9c83739bg3ddbg41c7g8892gbeab4fe98159": ["Holy hells. <i>Under-elf.</i>", "863d6788-5887-45c8-bafa-87128631904e", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "16e92092-fe45-c5df-553f-39125aa689a3"], "hcd3e575ag678bg4bcagb254g55b8fb73e5cc": ["Holy hells. <i>Under-dwarf.</i>", "863d6788-5887-45c8-bafa-87128631904e", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "e4e3299d-4bdc-6083-2ccb-3d368ca40522"], "ha88aecdag9ee0g468bg9495gdc3fa09f195e": ["Zorru was right. Yellow as a toad, and twice as ugly.", "863d6788-5887-45c8-bafa-87128631904e", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "b8d3c561-b566-45d8-b1f3-714c1ad9f277"], "hd35ac2c8g9cc5g48c0g9332g214ff5a7d640": ["Zorru was right. Yellow as a toad, and twice as ugly.", "863d6788-5887-45c8-bafa-87128631904e", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "fb88ba05-b0ca-df43-683f-fe2c3eda7a38"], "he7317dd9g12e9g47a5g8332g25725bbf23a3": ["Leave it alone, Damays.", "2c8537fb-bf73-43a2-a8ff-48e41453adea", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "722bb5d3-c01f-5c22-a52b-c8df79728b45"], "h400d87b7g8d1fg40acg9f19g5408f2d77003": ["*The captive's mouth is still, yet her voice is clear.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "163c8b51-790e-3854-ce79-cd1bf9b4f94c"], "h34577bb6g71dbg46e6g84b4g261a73eeebfc": ["The thing's dangerous. Leave it for the goblins to kill.", "2c8537fb-bf73-43a2-a8ff-48e41453adea", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "895f499c-384b-20cc-037c-490fd514122b"], "h27c99108gd8c3g4753gb9fbg6ae4b1491e72": ["And if it escapes? How will you - oh! A guest.", "863d6788-5887-45c8-bafa-87128631904e", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "8593a0bc-8c74-4698-f055-4ecba3bfcf29"], "h4e95c916gb929g4c70g9d9dg57884d52c553": ["<i>You again. Get rid of them.</i>", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "a024246f-81da-7f99-4ac2-c80f0c9f2243"], "hc5bbd9c8g214fg4912g8f80g92aa00fc5ec3": ["You abandoned me on the ship. Why should I help you?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "9bbf1769-161e-5977-0288-92203627cf30"], "h3b16c12fg9d8cg4114gb252g2f4d8f4ff540": ["You abandoned me on the ship. Why should I help you?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "42d73d65-3dfc-3584-b220-ef1f38a955b4"], "hb574cddfg8c94g439eg8589g7528ed3f6c9a": ["Rather demanding for a woman in your position. Why should I?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "ec9a98c1-58c0-c681-0125-b0bbb9dc6a08"], "h3ec0244fg4fccg4ec9gbf52gc749b0eea9a4": ["<i>A githyanki. She ought to be killed, here and now.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "6668a80b-7874-0b56-5e77-8435a60011cc"], "h3cb5eeb8g5f62g4836g9945g35cea941fcfe": ["He's right. No one's safe if that thing goes loose. Not even us.", "863d6788-5887-45c8-bafa-87128631904e", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "a379a495-db35-3db0-e469-3122deb77b0f"], "h838e56a7gf946g4b0agb3e2gef297694d5fb": ["She's right. No one's safe if that thing goes loose. Not even us.", "863d6788-5887-45c8-bafa-87128631904e", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "a379a495-db35-3db0-e469-3122deb77b0f"], "h99bc8d89gfd6eg4b53g90a4g787ccddbe00b": ["<i>Damays?</i>", "2c8537fb-bf73-43a2-a8ff-48e41453adea", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "b932f36f-2d7d-2fa5-2514-e22d3f07d90e"], "h8acee5f3g63ccg4e2egacb8ge7e42b4ee3eb": ["<i>Enough</i>. Lower the trap. Ready your blade.", "863d6788-5887-45c8-bafa-87128631904e", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "d2f14018-35f7-165f-990a-44854f4edf4b"], "hda3a4f7fg97ebg47b0g98d7g4ce73702ce1e": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "ba4784fa-304a-ce4e-dfc6-3365d44634dd"], "hb4234094g0709g4206g878agef6801fc0783": ["This creature is dangerous. Get out of here - leave it to me!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "77eb1601-729f-121a-48f6-c5c00a407d0b"], "hd77e3b06gcec3g4652gb114g2ea3a1e18220": ["He's right. Let's go - we need to check out that blast.", "863d6788-5887-45c8-bafa-87128631904e", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "89f21566-a576-a16c-18a0-35bc183f5943"], "hca35c797gfe3bg47fdga4fcg1b51cbd6d066": ["She's right. Let's go - we need to check out that blast.", "863d6788-5887-45c8-bafa-87128631904e", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "89f21566-a576-a16c-18a0-35bc183f5943"], "h73a848begdf59g42aega093g12e451921592": ["A blast? I could use more specifics.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "31f02080-718b-e3b4-f453-0a3c8633d52d"], "h98b7bd67gb599g4363g8f98g9997a2ec916f": ["You didn't hear it? Shook our camp good, so we came for a look.", "863d6788-5887-45c8-bafa-87128631904e", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "80ac0e01-114b-fb4f-4189-11f9b5396e5c"], "hdf011010gfa83g4876gb991g4d44f9330d6a": ["I'm in dire need of healing. Where is this camp?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "96f63ea3-f7e4-6eee-9178-8b933651f220"], "h96017eeeg4198g4e8fgbf1cg257162e07611": ["Nymessa. Come.", "863d6788-5887-45c8-bafa-87128631904e", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "e271e0cc-011c-f2fd-03ad-8658ffa31a5b"], "hb8b9ffc6gcf5bg4ee7g8ce4g2dcfcbb6d1de": ["Enough gawking - get me down.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "c5ede736-dd60-fcde-2baf-70a1e75dd273"], "h4222bc0ag58e9g4cd3ga849g614bc9919790": ["It will be done.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "11edf65a-dd6c-42fc-1593-cd2b64e66f66"], "he990c3e4ge94fg421ag9b58gbd1ee7280c43": ["Now that they're out of earshot, sure.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "fe3451ff-dcbc-5294-bf9e-742d25f1620b"], "h0d7295d2g3e54g45f4g8106g32d3f9665cc3": ["Say 'please'.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "d575e738-9d0a-36a2-1081-3846e53b3fe8"], "h8a291c64gd33dg4ea3g84e5g9970fa3213b2": ["Never.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "0c043773-b1d5-7b0f-53ba-2058d8a270d7"], "h643ffe40g5c19g444eg8141g27b7bbf3793c": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "317d85b7-a5d5-88d3-5219-6e857e37aa80"], "h5c623854gf38bg4949ga97dg1de9a09a1c0f": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "b0a56cad-4a3a-3523-8dd8-5a4873bb627c"], "hb3034de7gbd1fg438fga384gf2dc3677f9bd": ["Damays, let's...", "2c8537fb-bf73-43a2-a8ff-48e41453adea", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "e678917a-580b-3de6-7069-daf103be54b5"], "h2a0de624g9c18g4681g841dg5a9ccbe6723c": ["No. I'm not leaving this fiend with a stranger.", "863d6788-5887-45c8-bafa-87128631904e", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "f60c6130-d3fe-ec2f-e5dd-b0ca2dc2b526"], "hfa092444gba46g495ag906fg77ab22996355": ["<i>Kill them.</i>", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "4da01d6f-5ff8-9603-08b0-ffed20df2643"], "h5dbe9909g722fg4f98gacb2g739fcb6ac359": ["Shoot the trap down. We must kill it before it harms someone.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "830af8fd-872c-bee5-1621-12a3642a3069"], "heb213fedg99f6g4790gbf21gc24f38eddf00": ["<i>Damays?</i>", "2c8537fb-bf73-43a2-a8ff-48e41453adea", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "4547c681-3475-19dc-1346-0b936f768a13"], "h9988da27gcaf0g4edeg9c92g8c5071f3277d": ["No. We take it to camp. Zevlor will know what to do with it.", "863d6788-5887-45c8-bafa-87128631904e", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "4ac9ae47-90cb-eb8f-3bb5-7fbb95429955"], "hf06d624bg0b3bg44d7ga380ge3e4c04796bb": ["Shoot the trap down. I'll tear it apart before anyone else gets hurt.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "db75c733-4df6-7b24-00b3-6f31183cc7d5"], "h0e557a45g63d1g40e0g8522gd2c0cb327e10": ["<i>Attack the tieflings.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "2cff860d-5aba-04a9-6dfe-1864bab6e146"], "hf12bdb30g0caag4a7cgbf1fg4c7a46dbe9dd": ["Nymessa, watch out!", "863d6788-5887-45c8-bafa-87128631904e", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "98d2fa47-a7d0-7caa-b9e2-c256f924ba59"], "h80e8dc31gfc56g4364gb00egba2cb00eee85": ["<i>Ignore the sensations and leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "4a3f8e0a-a1f9-2781-c557-d4e342f8f5c3"], "h8f7561afg0b86g499bgb506ge63247ce9d86": ["Let's get the creature to camp. Then we'll look into the blast.", "863d6788-5887-45c8-bafa-87128631904e", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "e04ba53c-c6f2-bca3-e68e-261dc5172cae"], "h88c712bfg4ee3g4f05gb773g094edc82fd6b": ["Blades high, Nymessa.", "863d6788-5887-45c8-bafa-87128631904e", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "6302707b-ffeb-c3ea-5f12-c9a674337dec"], "h49230ffeg5c94g4359g8ceeg3b8c94a55b41": ["If you value your life, walk away.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "ea41d030-3cd5-6926-ba31-0c37922bafeb"], "hb6d5fdcdga539g4950ga1fcg52f9847a9a84": ["Damays...", "2c8537fb-bf73-43a2-a8ff-48e41453adea", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "008014ea-23a6-022f-e7b8-46afefb5b440"], "h593a4e37gc9e9g439eg8cfdg98a2c353c5da": ["Come, Nymessa. <i>Now.</i>", "863d6788-5887-45c8-bafa-87128631904e", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "b7b9f556-675c-d80f-d6fe-50025fc64bb9"], "ha11eee3cg8bf3g4e2dgb8a2gb381a3af818c": ["Not happening. Damays - now!", "2c8537fb-bf73-43a2-a8ff-48e41453adea", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_LaeZelRecruitment_TieflingsScene.html", "4d9770ef-455d-4621-b598-5f5662992a2c"]}